    <title>
      <Value><![CDATA[About Cow Paradise]]></Value>
    </title>
    <metaDescription>
      <Value><![CDATA[The story behind Cow Paradise -- from a napkin doodle to a cosmic universe of games, stories, and the Moo Family.]]></Value>
    </metaDescription>
    <blocks>
      <Value><![CDATA[{"contentData":[{"contentTypeKey":"f4a00001-0000-0000-0000-000000000001","key":"ab000001-0000-0000-0000-000000000001","values":[{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextBox","alias":"pageHeroSectionId","value":"about-hero","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.MediaPicker3","alias":"pageHeroBackgroundImage","value":"","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextBox","alias":"pageHeroBackgroundImageAlt","value":"The Story Behind Cow Paradise","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextBox","alias":"pageHeroEyebrow","value":"","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextBox","alias":"pageHeroHeading","value":"The Story Behind Cow Paradise","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextArea","alias":"pageHeroSubheading","value":"From a simple sketch to a cosmic phenomenon -- this is how Cow Paradise came to life.","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.MediaPicker3","alias":"pageHeroLogoImage","value":"","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextBox","alias":"pageHeroCtaPrimaryLabel","value":"","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextBox","alias":"pageHeroCtaPrimaryUrl","value":"","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.MediaPicker3","alias":"pageHeroCtaPrimaryImage","value":"","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextBox","alias":"pageHeroCtaSecondaryLabel","value":"","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextBox","alias":"pageHeroCtaSecondaryUrl","value":"","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.MediaPicker3","alias":"pageHeroCtaSecondaryImage","value":"","segment":null}]},{"contentTypeKey":"f4a00005-0000-0000-0000-000000000005","key":"ab000002-0000-0000-0000-000000000002","values":[{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextBox","alias":"richTextImageSectionId","value":"about-story","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextBox","alias":"richTextImageHeading","value":"About Us","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.RichText","alias":"richTextImageBody","value":"<p>At Cow Paradise, we craft playful worlds where every kid can learn, explore, and grow. Our games and stories follow the Moo Family -- six friendly characters who lead every adventure with curiosity, kindness, and play.</p><p>We started with a single doodle. Today, we're a small team building a universe that combines imaginative storytelling with hands-on learning -- letting kids be kids while quietly building real-world skills.</p>","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.MediaPicker3","alias":"richTextImageImage","value":"","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextBox","alias":"richTextImageImageAlt","value":"The Moo Family on the beach","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.DropDown.Flexible","alias":"richTextImagePosition","value":"[\"right\"]","segment":null}]},{"contentTypeKey":"f4a00006-0000-0000-0000-000000000006","key":"ab000003-0000-0000-0000-000000000003","values":[{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextBox","alias":"imgOverlaySectionId","value":"moo-journey","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.MediaPicker3","alias":"imgOverlayBackgroundImage","value":"","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextBox","alias":"imgOverlayBackgroundImageAlt","value":"The Moo Journey","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextBox","alias":"imgOverlayHeading","value":"THE MOO JOURNEY","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextArea","alias":"imgOverlaySubheading","value":"From Napkin Doodles to Game Hero","segment":null}]},{"contentTypeKey":"f4a0000d-0000-0000-0000-00000000000d","key":"ab000004-0000-0000-0000-000000000004","values":[{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextBox","alias":"impactTimelineSectionId","value":"impact-timeline","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextBox","alias":"impactTimelineHeading","value":"Our Impact","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.TextArea","alias":"impactTimelineSubheading","value":"Milestones from the Cow Paradise journey.","segment":null},{"culture":null,"editorAlias":"Umbraco.BlockList","alias":"impactTimelineCards","value":"{\"contentData\":[{\"contentTypeKey\":\"f4a00025-0000-0000-0000-000000000025\",\"key\":\"ad000101-0000-0000-0000-000000000101\",\"values\":[{\"culture\":null,\"editorAlias\":\"Umbraco.TextBox\",\"alias\":\"impactTimelineCardYear\",\"value\":\"2021\",\"segment\":null},{\"culture\":null,\"editorAlias\":\"Umbraco.TextBox\",\"alias\":\"impactTimelineCardTitle\",\"value\":\"Founded\",\"segment\":null},{\"culture\":null,\"editorAlias\":\"Umbraco.TextArea\",\"alias\":\"impactTimelineCardDescription\",\"value\":\"Cow Paradise begins with a single napkin sketch and a big idea.\",\"segment\":null},{\"culture\":null,\"editorAlias\":\"Umbraco.MediaPicker3\",\"alias\":\"impactTimelineCardIcon\",\"value\":\"\",\"segment\":null},{\"culture\":null,\"editorAlias\":\"Umbraco.TextBox\",\"alias\":\"impactTimelineCardAccentColor\",\"value\":\"#FFE9C5\",\"segment\":null}]},{\"contentTypeKey\":\"f4a00025-0000-0000-0000-000000000025\",\"key\":\"ad000102-0000-0000-0000-000000000102\",\"values\":[{\"culture\":null,\"editorAlias\":\"Umbraco.TextBox\",\"alias\":\"impactTimelineCardYear\",\"value\":\"2022\",\"segment\":null},{\"culture\":null,\"editorAlias\":\"Umbraco.TextBox\",\"alias\":\"impactTimelineCardTitle\",\"value\":\"First Game Released\",\"segment\":null},{\"culture\":null,\"editorAlias\":\"Umbraco.TextArea\",\"alias\":\"impactTimelineCardDescription\",\"value\":\"Cow Run launches and racks up a million plays in its first month.\",\"segment\":null},{\"culture\":null,\"editorAlias\":\"Umbraco.MediaPicker3\",\"alias\":\"impactTimelineCardIcon\",\"value\":\"\",\"segment\":null},{\"culture\":null,\"editorAlias\":\"Umbraco.TextBox\",\"alias\":\"impactTimelineCardAccentColor\",\"value\":\"#3FBD